messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签应为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "adapter_extraction 阶段在提取意图时，未能将 API 返回的原始意图编码 4001 正确映射到 customer_portrait；由于置信度低（0.5）或映射配置缺失，将其归类为 other，导致最终意图标签错误。label_mapping 仅继承该错误输出。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "data": {"intent": "other"}},
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "data": {"evidence_intent": "4001", "intent_match": false}},
        {"source": "runtime_checks", "data": {"actual_mapping": "other", "expected_intent": "customer_portrait"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "应提取目标产品实体",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别 API 未识别出查询中的产品实体“重疾险”，返回的 entities 为空，因此 adapter_extraction 无法提取 target_value。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "data": {"target_value": null}},
        {"source": "intent_evidence", "data": {"entities": []}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度应达到阈值",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "API 返回的意图置信度为 0.5，低于业务期望的 0.7 阈值，表明模型对用户查询的意图分类存在高度不确定性。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "data": {"confidence": 0.5}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "不应错误触发fallback",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "adapter_extraction 因为意图置信度低或未匹配已知意图，将结果标记为 subIntent=“其他意图”，实际上触发了 fallback 逻辑，导致用户查询被降级处理。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "data": {"subIntent": "其他意图"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "调度边界符合客户画像场景",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "最终 intent 为 other，导致调度系统将其路由到通用处理分支，而非客户画像分析流程。根本原因在于上游意图映射错误。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "data": {"intent": "other"}}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整体 contract 失败是由于 intent_api_call 对“上季度买了重疾险的客户画像”查询返回了错误的意图编码 4001 且未提取实体，adapter_extraction 在低置信度下将其错误降级为 other，label_mapping 继承该错误，导致与参考输出严重偏差。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "data": {"intent_match": false, "evidence_intent": "4001"}},
        {"source": "runtime_checks", "data": {"status": "failed", "root_cause_category": "label_mapping"}},
        {"source": "judge_result", "data": {"overall_fulfillment": "not_fulfilled"}}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别 API 对查询“帮我看看上季度买了重疾险的客户都是啥样的？”的错误识别（返回原始意图 4001，置信度 0.5，无实体），结合 adapter_extraction 的低置信度兜底映射策略，使意图被错误标记为 other，从而级联导致所有下游期望失败。label_mapping 仅传递该错误，未纠正。",
  "evidence": [
    {"source": "extracted_output", "summary": "intent=other, confidence=0.5, target_value=null"},
    {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "summary": "evidence_intent=4001, intent_match=false"},
    {"source": "runtime_checks", "summary": "raw_intent=None映射为other，而expected_intent=customer_portrait"},
    {"source": "judge_result", "summary": "所有业务期望未满足，整体判定 not_fulfilled"}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "high"
}

